subsection.p:
Every session bean provides the facility to override the default persistence context annotation declaration by modelling the following tagged values on the session bean class:
@andromda.service.persistence.context.unit.name Override the unit name for the default persistence context.
@andromda.service.persistence.context.unit.type Specifiy whether a trasaction scoped or extended scoped persistence context is required for the persistence context associated with the default entity manager.
